snippet.title: Jerry's Autowalking Adventure to Rescue His Cheese - Super Mario World Hack
snippet.description:
This Super Mario World hack is Green Jerry’s first finished and released Kaizo hack.

It features 7 levels, each one with their own theme, and has only 1 route, so there are no secret exits. And as you can see in the video, I am NOT exactly fit for Kaizo hacks.

Story:

Oh no! Tom has stolen Jerry’s cheese, and put a spell on him, and now he can’t stop walking! Jerry has to defeat him to undo the spell!

Tom & Jerry (C) Warner Bros Discovery
Hack developed by Green Jerry
Download: https://www.romhacking.net/hacks/8249/
